### Version

Yosys 0.38+120 (git sha1 1e42b4f0f, clang++ 11.1.0 -fPIC -Os)

### On which OS did this happen?

macOS

### Reproduction Steps

```
read_verilog <<EOF
module top(a, b, y);
	input wire a;
	input wire b;
	output wire y;

	wire j = k ? a : ~k;
	wire k = l ? ~j : b;
	wire l = j ? ~k : b;

	assign y = l;
endmodule
EOF
share
```

### Expected Behavior

`share` not stuck

### Actual Behavior

`share` stuck

